The paper discusses the selection, development, and comparison of machine learning methods in data mining, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of benchmark datasets and the analysis of their diversity and performance also suggest a connection to data science (cs.DS), computer vision (cs.CV), and natural language processing (cs.CL).
